				<div class="postbody">
				I think that we should enforce a China-esque stander for abortions.... meaning that it is still considered non living and non murderous to abort the useless  or unwanted fetus uptill the fetus's first breath of air.  
<br />

<br />
Some background info. China's government has declaired it illegal to have more than one offspring per couple. Due to cultural background more and more female fetus's are being aborted way late into the trimester in hopes of the next child being male.  If a government health agent/worker catches a mother bearing a second child they will force her to have an abortion...
<br />

<br />

<br />
While I might change the methods the Chinese would use (10CCs of Fermaldahyde into the brain when the crown of head pokes through) I think that this carefree or unregulated form of birth control could potentially have positive effects on the US and the population it has.  
<br />

<br />
For one, poor people and people who shouldnt have kids could have them aborted.  The welfare-mother of 12 and has another one in 2 weeks doesnt need that child so kill it. Save tax payers money and the suffering of the child living in an impoverished/neglected life which more than likely would lead to crime.  
<br />
Also there needs to be some form of regulated abortions for people with handicaps.  Simple enough, severly mentally retarded and/or mentally disabled people to not need to reproduce and share this loving gift of Downs or what not with their new born child. Again this would save some poor child from having what I would consider a horrible life.  
<br />

<br />
Now Im not saying abort every baby by all means, or even going as far as a GATTACA movie type screening w/ valids and invalids.  If the recessive genes from the two parents happend to be unlucky and they have a defective child, they can have it. Im just saying that the parents should be healthy people.  As for the inadaquate lifestyle for abortions (eg poor) this could be more regulated by like, of Co-op City mother, you have 5 kids, are unwed, have no job, and are having a 6th... WHY... kill that little bundle of joy and done with it, all this kid would do is crime and then bitch about how the white man kept him down because his mother got herself knocked up while sellingherself for crack.  
<br />

<br />
Its common sense and should be followed so we dont have a degrading gene pool.... In the past, the defective would not have lived and their defective genes were lost because they did not produce offspring.  Now with modern technology and the cultural values we have now, it is wrong to cull these defects and instead we encourage them to prosper to their highest (which isnt that high) goals.  Many developed countries still practice some form of this removing the bad seeds.  India will leash mentally ill kids outside till they die (im not for this act, just showing examples) and in other Asia-Pacifica countries, they are shunned as pariahs and recieve no help and then die.  
<br />

<br />
This could make the world a better place, the human race stronger, and will by all means have some sort unity knowing that when you decide to have kids the chances of them being retarded or born into a bad lifestyle is nill due to regulations and the fact that the genes arent there (for the first example)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Yaksa "This is like Hitlers Master plan in a way" LoveCraft
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
PS. This is for Trysbrina.<br />
				<span class="gensmall"></span><br />
